Blackbird logging is useful for debugging any javascript application and can be thought of as a log4js.

This plugins adds blackbird logging to any grails application and simply provides a tag to add the necessary resources ( CSS, JS and images ) bundled into a easily installable plugin.

To use the plugin:

	grails install-plugin ###

Add the following taglib to the head of the pages/layout to import required resources

	<blackbird: resources />

	
